video_title: 5 Signs Of A Highly Sensitive Person | Dr Julie
transcript:
here's five signs of a highly sensitive
person number one other people's moods
and pain affect you deeply
two when you're in a busy environment
you often feel the need to withdraw and
be alone to get relief from the
stimulation of those surroundings
three when people try to get you to do
too many things at once you quickly
become overwhelmed by all the demands
four you hate change and avoid having a
lot going on because of all the strong
emotions that come with it
five when you have to compete or perform
in front of other people you become so
nervous that you do much worse than you
would otherwise
